{"tid":1072813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子街頭飛來艷福　闢室談心遭搶金鏈","createTime":"2019-03-22T09:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T09:09:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7ccf85ac4ded1c283ebdb39aa01dc06cf1a49832","tid":1072813,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T09:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322121840150-0322_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190322163123\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322121840150-0322_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190322163123&h=1a57c03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣發生盜竊案！今早（22日）11時許，一名姓張（62歲）男子行經川龍街71號對開，被一名操普通話的女子兜搭，兩人言談甚歡，遂一起到對開大廈劏房闢室談心。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，當張擬寬衣之際，有人突然搶去他身上一條約值5萬港元的金鏈，繼而奪門逃去。事主大為驚愕，只好穿回衣服落樓追尋女賊蹤影，惟對方已沿荃灣街市街方向逃去無蹤，張無奈報警求助。 <br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕至，用警車接載事主在區內兜截，惜暫無發現，經初步調查後，案件列作「盜竊」，交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊跟進，正翻查相關「天眼」錄影片段，追緝一名身高約1.6米、中等身材，案發時身穿白色上衣及深色裙的女子歸案。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/bkn-20190322121840150-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fbkn-20190322121840150-0322_00822_001.html&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=cbdf4415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/bkn-20190322121840150-0322_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ed51f6f4e4e5d5e4d413dff6f71097016cb7bb2d","tid":1072813,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抵死啦死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n爛鳩金鍊五皮野隨時廢老專作大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呀伯一定以為自己好靚仔"},{"pid":"5b48ba9c7a4223cb6e85657ecad4c53aeaf03499","tid":1072813,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci